formula: Let b(q) be the determinant of the 3 X 3 Hankel matrix [E_6, E_8, E_10 ; E_8, E_10, E_12 ; E_10, E_12, E_14]. G.f. is -691＾2*b(q)/(1728^2*250＾2).
